## Success Criteria

From `plans/mem-optimize-v5.md`, refined:

| Metric | Target | When |
|--------|--------|------|
| Tag anchor coverage (both `type:` + `domain:`) | >= 80% | After Phase 1 Step 5a |
| Tag diversity (no single tag > 25%) | Pass | After Phase 1 Step 5a |
| Claude-as-judge weighted average | >= 3.5/5 | After Phase 1 Step 9 |
| A/B improvement (Phase 0 prompt vs baseline) | >= 15% tag quality improvement | After Phase 1 Step 8 |
| Recall Precision@5 | >= 0.6 | After Phase 2 deployed |
| Recall MRR | >= 0.7 | After Phase 2 deployed |
| Stale memories (>90 days, 0 access) | < 10% of active | After Phase 2 monthly cron running |
| Semantic duplicates | < 5% of active | After quarterly dedup sweep |

