## Cost

| Component | Cost | Cadence |
|-----------|------|---------|
| Monthly quality scoring (GPT-4.1-mini, 30 memories) | ~$0.01 | Monthly |
| Monthly tag analysis (pure Python) | $0.00 | Monthly |
| Monthly recall benchmark (Azure Search queries) | $0.00 | Monthly |
| Quarterly A/B comparison (GPT-5.2, 8 sessions x2) | ~$1.40 | Quarterly |
| Quarterly semantic dedup sweep (GPT-4.1-mini) | ~$0.05 | Quarterly |
| Quarterly permanent review (manual) | $0.00 | Quarterly |
| Azure AI Search (basic tier, flat-rate) | ~$74/mo | Ongoing (already running) |
| **Total incremental cost** | **~$6/year** | |

