        → Dedup (112→68) → Normalize → Pin/lifecycle/health monitor
        ↓
DONE:   Phase 1b — Extraction Prompt Tuning                           ✅ 2026-03-28
        5-layer A/B test → L1+L2 won (+12.8%) → Re-tag 68 memories
        → Azure scoring profile (80-day quadratic freshness + importance)
        → Env var DB path fix (no more post-deploy sed)
        ↓
NEXT:   Phase 2 — Package into Skill (ClawBot target)
        Build skill dir → CLI → Cron → Deploy to VM → Verify
        ↓
LATER:  Phase 3 — Claude Code Target
        RESEARCH AGAIN (Claude Code context is different) → Schema check → Config tuning → Deploy to Mac
        ↓
FUTURE: ProMem iterative extraction (73.8% recall vs 41% one-shot)
        ↓
ONGOING: Each cycle starts with RESEARCH before any changes
         Monthly report → Research what's new → Adjust approach → Execute
```

